es’ Court sitting at Audu Bako Secretariat, Kano, for allegedly sexually abusing nine under-age boys. September 7, 2016 In "News" A 28-year-old man, Alhassan Musa, on Wednesday appeared in a Magistrates’ Court sitting at Audu Bako Secretariat, Kano, for allegedly sexually abusing nine under-age boys. September 7, 2016 In "News"